data.description: Gorgeous former model home with owed Solar in Juliana's Garden. This pristine property is a show stopper inside and out. The backyard is designed to entertain guest with 2 wood pergolas, custom fountain, lush landscaping with new sod, and granite bar. Interior amenities include designer wall treatments in most rooms, large kitchen with black and stainless appliances, fireplace, shutters, decorative tile flooring, and private master patio. We can't forget the communities private park and gardens. Schedule your private showing today to view this designer home.
